              "action": "Alcoholism; Book Trade; Bookbinders; Booksellers; Dying People, Invoked By; Fire Fighters; Heart Patients; Hospital Workers; Hospitals; Nurses; Printers; Sick; Tultepac, Mexico",
              "tags": "fighters heart patients alcoholism john book trade bookbinders nurses people printers sick tultepac fire dying god hospitals workers mexico hospital booksellers"
