              "action": "<p>\n Supposedly the first\n <a href=\"https://www.catholic.org/encyclopedia/view.php?id=2927\">\n  Christian\n </a>\n missionary to preach in\n <a href=\"https://www.catholic.org/encyclopedia/view.php?id=10800\">\n  Sicily\n </a>\n Although almost certainly a legendary figure, he is venerated in the hill town of Agirone, Sicily.\n</p>\n",
