              "action": "<p>\n Bishop of Astorga, Spain, formerly a Benedictine\n <a href=\"https://www.catholic.org/encyclopedia/view.php?id=8107\">\n  monk\n </a>\n at Argeo, Spain. He was also\n <a href=\"https://www.catholic.org/encyclopedia/view.php?id=22\">\n  abbot\n </a>\n of San Pedro de Montes at Vierzo. Named\n <a href=\"https://www.catholic.org/encyclopedia/view.php?id=1918\">\n  bishop\n </a>\n in 895, he built many institutions in that diocese. In 931, Gennadius resigned and lived as a recluse until his death.\n</p>\n",
